Consent is s3xy 🌹

Do you feel the difference when a man asks to kiss or touch you? 

It feels like respect 

To be asked and not assumed 

While I do believe there are moments in flow for taking intuitive actions, it’s still nice to ask 

Consent creates trust between two people (this applies to new friendships too) 

It gives us a moment to reflect, decide and vocalize what we feel comfortable with and are ready for 

Physical touch is an exchange of energy. We get to choose who we want to exchange that with

My body is my temple. And I decide who I allow to touch, hug, cuddle, kiss and play with 🦋
